name: Ging Gong Kaew
description: Ging, Gong and Kaew. The cute Capybara siblings newly named at Khao Kheow Zoo. The naming process had a total of 94000 votes and posts with these capybaras has surpassed 1 million views. Every day there are posts of them exceeding 100000 views. We believe in time there will be international interest in these animals similar to the phenomenon of Moo Deng the Pygmy Hippo This is a memecoin on Solana with a growing and active community
